icle class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zcq1719661703205.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zcq1719661703205.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ens1665702754427\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /dataonly\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create entities and models.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ens1665702754427__section_w1086ab1b5b1_w1087ab1b5_w1088ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ens1665702754427__p_d148496e1_d148497e1_d148498e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/dataonly</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ens1665702754427__section_w1089ab1b5b3_w1090ab1b5_w1091ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1155669e60\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ens1665702754427__d6988e20\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"khj1665702753156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/khj1665702753156.html\" title=\"Import interface definitions to integrate call-out to web services, various types of middleware, or to generate C call-in stub code for all types of components.\">/sti</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ens1665702754427__section_w1092ab1b5b5_w1093ab1b5_w1094ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1155669e76\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ens1665702754427__p_d148508e1_d148509e1_d148510e1\">Creates entities and models only, without creating signatures. If used in combination with other switches, this switch takes precedence over <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmr1719655329263.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmr1719655329263.html\" title=\"Checks syntax only. No signatures, entities, or occurrences are updated or added.\">/nosig</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7425084\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7425084\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/dataonly Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /dataonly Create entities and models. /dataonly Used With /sti Description Creates entities and models only, without creating signatures. If used in combination with other switches, this switch takes precedence over /nosig . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}